Title(2, "Programming Language");
Format("^IHer. suggestion: `Begin with assembly (like^i ^Mi-8086^m ^INASM) firstly, then come here. It is notable that advanced languages began from mapping with assembly.'^i\n");
Format("^BOpposite Points of C and C++^b\n");
ListBegin("itemize");
	ListItem("", "The length of ^Mint^m, ^Mlong^m varies with the architecture\n\t\tand is independent of ^Mstduint^m.");
ListEnd();

